<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f53d.png" alt="🔽" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f53d.png" alt="🔽" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f53d.png" alt="🔽" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p>



